                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-834-18470301 t18470301-834-punishment-186"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Edward Bullock, Esq.</hi>
